  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK962">
<l>cīriṉuñ cīralla ceyyārē cīroṭu </l>
<l>pērāṇmai vēṇṭu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who desire (to maintain their) honour, will surely do nothing dishonourable, even for the sake of fame.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
